CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: The Funds primary investment objective is current income exempt from regular U.S. federal income taxes. Fund will seek to achieve its investment objectives by investing, directly or indirectly, at least 80% of its Managed Assets in municipal bonds, the interest on which is, in the opinion of bond counsel to the issuers, generally excludable from gross income for regular U.S. federal income tax purposes, except that the interest may be includable in taxable income for purposes of the Federal alternative minimum tax.
